articles.author: Sam McNeil
articles.title: Luxembourg crowns a new grand duke after the former grand duke abdicates - AP News
articles.description: Grand Duke Guillaume has ascended to the throne of Luxembourg after swearing an oath in a traditional ceremony on Friday. Guillaume takes over from his father, Henri, who served for 25 years. The ceremony was attended by royals and European heads of state. In…
articles.content:
LUXEMBOURG (AP) Grand Duke Guillaume swore an oath to ascend to the throne of Luxembourg on Friday in a traditional ceremony attended by royals and European heads of state.
